<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat Chuncz Schelm,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, in klagsweise fürbraht ein czetteln, die wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit
                            <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> hirynne
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>, und wer dem also, so deuht uns, daz
                        dem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwaz <expan>ungütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        geschehe. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>darynne czum <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan></add> durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>furderl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein wöllt</add>, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
